<document>
    <header>
        <title>Entries Administation Plugin</title>
    </header>

    <body>
        <section>
            <title>Description</title>
            <p>
                The Categories Administration plugin allows you to add new entries, modify existing entries,
                and delete entries from your blog. You are also allowed to delete comments and trackbacks when
                editing entries.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <title>Installation and Setup</title>
            <p>
                In your global
                <code>plugin.properties</code> file, add the following line:
            </p>
            <source>
                edit-blog-entries=org.blojsom.plugin.admin.EditBlogEntriesPlugin
            </source>
        </section>
        <section>
            <title>Usage</title>
            <p>
                After logging into the administration console, you may click on the link to "Edit Blog Entries"
                and you will be able to add, modify, and delete entries.
            </p>
        </section>
    </body>
</document>

